--------------------------------------------------------------------
grok reads a cell and does a thing
munge does a thing.
munge and grok both have an operation in common
--------------------------------------------------------------------


munge uporablja isti skriti observer register, ki ga nastavlja grok

anchor = (9,8)
anchorValue = 0xc4

Invariant :
col7 + anchor c4 + 3-char prefix + sadni/adjective payload + XOR observer state


grok je XOR observer, ki nastavi skriti previous-cell register.
munge uporablja isti register.

Berljivi nizi so v relativnem dumpu pri anchorju 0xc4, stolpec x=7.
Nizi imajo obliko: 3-mestni prefix + pridevnik/stanje + sadje.
Ker se rezultat začne pri (7,3), sva s grok(7,3) nastavila register.
Po munge se isti stolpec transformira v končni password.


observation = previous XOR current    [grok]
observation = raw(x,y) XOR raw(x,y)   [grok]
observation = 00					  [munge]


beri stolpec x = 7 navpično
format = 3 znaki prefixa + opis (pridevnik stanja) + sadje

prefix tipa XXX  ; X ∈ (0...9)
opis stanja (string)
sadje (string)

Primer: {x: 7, y: 0} anchor: {x: 9, y: 8}
260goodcherries
Primer: {x: 7, y: 1} anchor: {x: 9, y: 8}
715ripepineapples
Primer: {x: 7, y: 2} anchor: {x: 9, y: 8}
789deliciousapples
Primer: {x: 7, y: 3} anchor: {x: 9, y: 8}
908badoranges
Primer: {x: 7, y: 4} anchor: {x: 9, y: 8}
489rottencarrots
Primer: {x: 8, y: 0} anchor: {x: 9, y: 8}
228blandpears
Primer: {x: 8, y: 1} anchor: {x: 9, y: 8}
.
.
.
.


grok(7,3) -> nastavi register
munge()   -> uporabi register
col7      -> razkrije password
submit    -> odklene level 41


